org.diachron.detection.utils

Class ChangesDetector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.diachron.detection.utils.ChangesDetector

  • public class ChangesDetector
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for the change detection between two named graph versions. The change detection considers a set of SPARQL update queries (one per change type) and populates accordingly a named graph which is called changes ontology. The detected changes are stored w.r.t. a changes ontology schema.
